    "image": "",
    "answer": "b",
    "solution": "Cos θ° = t<sup>2</sup> + t<sup>2</sup> -(√3t)<sup>2</sup> 2 x t x t\n\n= 2t<sup>2</sup> - 3t<sup>2</sup> 2t<sup>2</sup>\n= -t<sup>2</sup>/2t<sup>2</sup>\n= -1/2\n\nThus θ = cos<sup>-1</sup> (-0.5) = 120°",
